original_title: 羞恥 ある日突然男女社員混合 強●OL健康診断2021 スペシャル 2枚組 松本いちか
overview: At that time, I doubted my ears because the director of the personnel department said, "Because of the deterioration of business performance due to the Korona-ka, this year's health examination will be conducted by both men and women." Are you naked in front of a colleague or a male employee of your subordinates watching? That's impossible! The medical examination conducted in a venue as small as a conference room was not allowed to be naked ... My breasts were rubbed and my labia minora and vagina were unreservedly widened ... A suspicious instrument that I had never had was inserted with a slurp. Is it some kind of illness that the heart squeaks in the back of the head with embarrassment, but the back of the uterus gets moisturized?
title: Shame Business Woman Gets An Unexpected Health Checkup In Front Of Her Male Coworkers 2021
